sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant RemixRouter
    participant Route
    participant Component
    participant ReactQuery
    participant API
    participant State

    Browser->>RemixRouter: Navigate to URL
    RemixRouter->>Route: Load Route Component
    Route->>Component: Render UI Components

    alt Data Fetching Required
        Component->>ReactQuery: useQuery Hook
        ReactQuery->>API: Fetch Data
        API-->>ReactQuery: Return Response
        ReactQuery->>State: Cache Response
        ReactQuery-->>Component: Provide Data
    end

    Component->>Component: Local State Updates

    alt User Interaction
        Browser->>Component: User Action
        Component->>ReactQuery: useMutation Hook
        ReactQuery->>API: Send Mutation
        API-->>ReactQuery: Success/Error
        ReactQuery->>State: Update Cache
        ReactQuery-->>Component: Update UI
    end

    Component-->>Browser: Render Updated UI

    Note over ReactQuery,State: TanStack Query manages<br/>caching and synchronization
    Note over Component: Components use Radix UI<br/>and Tailwind styling
